China and Kuwait have agreed to work on a five-year cooperation plan, covering agriculture, 5G communications, and other high-tech areas. CGTN's Dong Xue sat down with Kuwaiti Foreign Minister and Minister of State for Cabinet Affairs, H.E. Sheikh/Dr. Ahmed Nasser Al-Mohammed Al-Ahmed Al-Jaber Al-Sabah, to hear his views on the bilateral ties and China's role in the Middle East.